Be loyal to those that give you that same type of respect back. TAG someone to this video that needs it! And text me 817.242.2719 if this touched your heart. #trentshelton #loyalty #inspiration

node.text:
𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘧𝘦𝘦𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴.⁣
⁣
𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇 𝐡𝐨𝐰 𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟 𝐟𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐭𝐨𝐱𝐢𝐜 𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐡𝐚𝐬 𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐩𝐞𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐥𝐢𝐟𝐞⁣
⁣
•𝐑𝐄𝐇𝐀𝐁 𝐒𝐄𝐒𝐒𝐈𝐎𝐍•⁣
Sometimes it’s necessary in your life to “UNPLUG” from situations that’s doing nothing but connecting you to pain, stress, and anger. People might call you difficult because you choose not to stay connected to something that isn’t for your life. Always remember, there’s nothing wrong with prioritizing your peace and having enough self-awareness to know that something is toxic for your life. ⁣
⁣
𝘛𝘈𝘎 𝘈 𝘍𝘙𝘐𝘌𝘕𝘋 𝘛𝘏𝘈𝘛 𝘕𝘌𝘌𝘋𝘚 𝘛𝘖 𝘚𝘌𝘌 𝘛𝘏𝘐𝘚

node.text:
𝘐 𝘯𝘦𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘪𝘴 𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘦. ⁣⁣
⁣
Drop a 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇🏾 with an upgrade 𝐆𝐨𝐝 blessed you with!!! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
•𝐑𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐛 𝐒𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧• ⁣⁣
I need you to understand sometimes you have to lose certain things, so God can bless you with better things. Certain things HAVE TO end so better things can begin. The storm never makes sense until you see the growth it produced. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Remember, sometimes the best way to add to your life is to subtract from it 🤷🏾‍♂️⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣
#trentshelton #faith #rehabtime #god #blessings #blessed #relationshipquotes #love #confidence #fortworth #texas #loveyourself #real

Drop a ❤️ if you believe in hard work! 

Progression is an ugly road that leads to a beautiful place. Plant the seed. Water the seed. Be patient. Reap the harvest. 

This motto is something we instill to our athletes and so much more. 

Live It. Breathe It. Be It. 

Lets get it! 

Shot by: @ethan.wldn 

#youthfootball #7on7 #texas #dfw #rehabtime #rarebreedacademy #football #sports

𝘐 𝘯𝘦𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘪𝘴 𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘦. ⁣⁣
⁣
Drop a 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇🏾 with an upgrade 𝐆𝐨𝐝 blessed you with!!! ⁣

Sometimes the best way God adds to your life is to subtract from it. Sometimes things have to happen that will immediately hurt your heart, but eventually heal your soul. Faith doesn’t mean it makes sense in the moment, it means that it will work out for the good of your life.
